00:22:42,415 --> 00:22:44,504
m'hot zey ile av-... yo, yo.

403
00:22:44,250 --> 00:22:46,154
ir gedenkt zeyere familyes?

404
00:22:44,504 --> 00:22:46,980
mi- i-... neyn.

405
00:22:47,123 --> 00:22:50,500
ikh gedenk, m'hot z⟨i⟩ gerufn Sh⟨UNK⟩ Koyen.

406
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:52,786
Koyen efsher iz geven di familye.

407
00:22:52,962 --> 00:22:55,580
dos iz a groyse kleyt geven,

408
00:22:55,580 --> 00:22:58,727
vos mayn tate fleg koyfn dort far der pekarnye

409
00:22:59,020 --> 00:23:02,743
mel, tsuker, vos m'hot gedarft. dos gedenk ikh.

410
00:23:02,952 --> 00:23:04,194
UNK

411
00:23:03,137 --> 00:23:05,560
nor vayter gedenk ikh nisht.

412
00:23:04,622 --> 00:23:09,780
ir gedenkt, zay- zaynen zey ibergeblibn lebn? dos veyst ir nit? zey hobn nit ge- ir hot zey nit getrofn?

413
00:23:07,238 --> 00:23:09,915
NO, m'hot zey avekgeshikt keyn Sibir.

414
00:23:09,921 --> 00:23:14,690
vi azoy zey zenen gelign in di betn, azoy hot men zey aroysgenemen un avekgeshikt,

415
00:23:14,781 --> 00:23:18,555
un ⟨o-⟩ keyn hemd afile nisht gelozt nemen, gornisht.

416
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:20,259
vi hot ir zikh dervust vegn dem?

417
00:23:20,164 --> 00:23:20,910
ha?

418
00:23:20,738 --> 00:23:22,031
vi hot ir...

419
00:23:20,910 --> 00:23:23,111
m'hot zikh dervust dem andern tog;

420
00:23:23,168 --> 00:23:25,038
m'iz aroysgegan in gas arayn,

421
00:23:25,038 --> 00:23:26,903
iz keyn mentsh nisht geven.

422
00:23:26,903 --> 00:23:29,456
di gantse gas iz geven oyfgehoybn

423
00:23:29,698 --> 00:23:32,847
un avekgeshikt, un oysgeramt di kleytn:

424
00:23:32,922 --> 00:23:35,011
gornisht geven in di kleytn.

425
00:23:35,011 --> 00:23:37,711
m'hot shoyn nisht gehat vu tsu koyfn a shtikl broyt,

426
00:23:37,711 --> 00:23:40,080
ver s'hot gornit gehat in shtub.

427
00:23:41,072 --> 00:23:48,204
hot ir gehert far der milkhome vegn Daytshland, vegn di Natsis, Natsistn, vegn Hitlern?

428
00:23:47,367 --> 00:23:49,660
ikh gedenk, ikh hob,

429
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:53,199
bin gegan tsum Prut. mir ze'mir zikh gegan bodn.

430
00:23:53,323 --> 00:23:55,910
gedenk ikh, lebn der zhandarmerye

431
00:23:55,910 --> 00:23:59,125
iz geshtanen a akht furlekh mit mentshn,

432
00:23:59,125 --> 00:24:01,468
vos zenen shoyn geven antlofene.

433
00:24:02,115 --> 00:24:05,079
oder ver, vos, hobn mi- hob ikh nit gevust;

434
00:24:05,203 --> 00:24:08,750
bin ⟨no⟩kh geven tsu yung zikh tsu visn fun azoyne zakhn.

435
00:24:09,388 --> 00:24:14,107
kh'gedenk, s'iz geshtanen dortn etlekhe furlekh mit mentshn, sa- yidn,

436
00:24:14,502 --> 00:24:19,283
ongegruzet, mit di kinder, mit zek, ongeleygt dort UNK. zet oys, zey hobn nokh

437
00:24:19,283 --> 00:24:22,580
gekont mitnemen a bisl zakhn mit zikh.

438
00:24:23,007 --> 00:24:24,510
dos gedenk ikh.

439
00:24:24,508 --> 00:24:27,190
zaynen, fun vanen zey zaynen gelofn v⟨eyst ir nit⟩?

440
00:24:25,791 --> 00:24:28,410
fun vanen zey zenen gelofn veys ikh nisht.

441
00:24:28,187 --> 00:24:30,678
un dos iz alts geven far der milkhome nokh?

442
00:24:29,930 --> 00:24:32,130
dos iz far der milkhome geven.

443
00:24:37,722 --> 00:24:41,951
vi iz forgekumen, vi hot ir zikh dervust, vi hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome?

444
00:24:42,379 --> 00:24:46,102
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome dem tsvey un tsvontsiktn JUNE,

445
00:24:47,323 --> 00:24:49,880
geven a fir a zeyger far tog,

446
00:24:50,665 --> 00:24:52,341
mir ze'mir nokh geshlofn,

447
00:24:52,341 --> 00:24:53,865
gelign in di betn,

448
00:24:54,107 --> 00:24:57,425
hot ongehoybn flien snaradn ibern kop.

449
00:24:57,448 --> 00:24:59,380
mir ho'mir gevoynt

450
00:24:59,406 --> 00:25:00,733
in Lipkan.

451
00:25:01,482 --> 00:25:05,627
in Lipkan iz geven di grenets keyn ⟨Radahuts⟩.

452
00:25:05,717 --> 00:25:08,039
⟨Radavuts⟩ iz geven Rumenye.

453
00:25:09,497 --> 00:25:11,111
un mir hobn gevoynt

454
00:25:11,134 --> 00:25:14,570
in Lipkan, un s'iz geven a brik aribertsugeyn.

455
00:25:15,808 --> 00:25:21,050
dortn zenen geven shoyn di daytshn mit di Rumener, tsuzamen,

456
00:25:21,192 --> 00:25:23,076
un zey hobn ongehoybn

457
00:25:23,115 --> 00:25:25,980
tsu shisn iber, keyn Lipkan,

458
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:28,374
in der shtot arayn, mit snaradn.

459
00:25:29,410 --> 00:25:32,590
un di snaradn zenen gefloygn ibern kop.

460
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:35,557
m'hot nit gekont afile fun der shtub aroysgeyn,

461
00:25:35,557 --> 00:25:38,077
un shtiber hobn shoyn ongehoybn brenen.

462
00:25:38,775 --> 00:25:40,704
geshosn hot men geshosn

463
00:25:40,704 --> 00:25:42,599
in mitn der shtot.

464
00:25:42,893 --> 00:25:46,684
dort hot men gevust az se voynen di, di komunistn.

465
00:25:49,002 --> 00:25:53,730
un den hot der tate ayngeshpant dos fe- f- di ferd

466
00:25:53,777 --> 00:25:56,449
un er hot undz ile aroyfgevarfn oyf der fur,

467
00:25:56,449 --> 00:25:58,952
un m'hot zikh genemen antloyfn fun Lipkan.

468
00:25:59,970 --> 00:26:03,811
m'iz antlofn finef un tsvontsik kilometer keyn Britshan.

469
00:26:04,628 --> 00:26:07,820
in Britshan hot mayn tate gehat a gutn-bruder,

470
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:10,410
un er hot undz geton a loz arayn tsun im,

471
00:26:10,686 --> 00:26:14,243
un er iz geforn krik az er zol nemen dem bagazh.

472
00:26:14,243 --> 00:26:16,226
er hot gemeynt, er vet nokh epes nemen.

473
00:26:16,226 --> 00:26:19,790
er iz tsugekumen, hot er gezen, undzer shtub ⟨iz,⟩ brent,

474
00:26:20,203 --> 00:26:24,264
un s'iz shoyn alding oysgeramt, iz er krik avek keyn Britshan.

475
00:26:24,777 --> 00:26:27,820
ze'mir avek keyn Britshan. dort vu mir ze'mir geven

476
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:29,861
iz geven punkt bayn veg,

477
00:26:29,861 --> 00:26:32,432
vos di komunistn hobn ongehoybn loyfn...

478
00:26:33,197 --> 00:26:35,505
di Kuzistn, di Kuzistn

479
00:26:35,505 --> 00:26:38,506
hobn ongehoybn loyfn oyf tsu rabeven di yidn.

480
00:26:38,547 --> 00:26:40,718
tsu hargenen, tsu rabeven.

481
00:26:40,858 --> 00:26:43,460
hot der khaver mayn tatn's gezogt,

482
00:26:43,491 --> 00:26:45,664
"Zeydl, nem di kinder

483
00:26:45,664 --> 00:26:47,082
mit UNK Rosye

484
00:26:47,082 --> 00:26:49,746
un gey avek in der un der shil arayn.

485
00:26:50,005 --> 00:26:54,082
ir tort nisht zayn do bayn veg." er hot mitgegibn zayn vayb oykhet,

486
00:26:54,173 --> 00:26:56,006
un di shv- shviger.

487
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:59,618
mir zenen avekgegan ot dort, me zol nisht zayn bayn veg.

488
00:27:00,231 --> 00:27:02,419
mir ze'mir geven in der shil

489
00:27:02,948 --> 00:27:04,760
a fir, finef tog.

490
00:27:05,344 --> 00:27:07,633
iz ongekumen a prikaz

491
00:27:07,639 --> 00:27:09,467
az ile Lipkaner

492
00:27:09,467 --> 00:27:13,168
zoln aroysgeyn oyf der tolike fun der pozharne,

493
00:27:13,984 --> 00:27:16,104
aza plats a groys.

494
00:27:17,578 --> 00:27:21,878
blaybn hot men moyre gehat, vayl, m'hot gezogt, tomer vet blaybn

495
00:27:21,878 --> 00:27:24,457
emetser fun di Lipkaner in Britshan,

496
00:27:25,105 --> 00:27:26,753
vet men undz shisn.

497
00:27:26,792 --> 00:27:29,216
ver hot gegebn aza bafel, aza prikaz?

498
00:27:28,058 --> 00:27:29,830
di Rumener.

499
00:27:29,914 --> 00:27:33,250
di Rumener hobn shoyn bafelt.

500
00:27:34,150 --> 00:27:37,519
den iz men aroysgegan yeder oyf der tolike,

501
00:27:37,812 --> 00:27:39,540
ile Lipkaner.

502
00:27:39,583 --> 00:27:43,542
s'iz a gantse shtot mit mentshn geven, zeyer a sakh mentshn.

503
00:27:44,730 --> 00:27:47,306
un der eybershter hot undz gegibn a regn,

504
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:51,060
az m'iz geshtanen iber di knies in vaser.

505
00:27:51,767 --> 00:27:54,073
un m'hot undz ile tsunoyfgenemen.

506
00:27:55,243 --> 00:27:59,877
un s'iz geven a tsvelef Rumener mit a akht daytshn,

507
00:27:59,884 --> 00:28:02,680
un m'hot undz ongehoybn traybn oyf di vegn.

508
00:28:03,023 --> 00:28:05,025
aroysgetribn fun Britshan,

509
00:28:05,048 --> 00:28:08,720
gegan in vaser un in blote biz in di knies arayn.

510
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:12,530
di kinder hobn geveynt, hungerike geven

511
00:28:12,928 --> 00:28:15,082
zeyer, yeder eyner.

512
00:28:16,725 --> 00:28:20,360
un m'hot undz getribn iber tol un iber berg,

513
00:28:21,214 --> 00:28:25,038
durkh di derfer; nisht gelozt undz arayngeyn durkhn dorf,

514
00:28:25,062 --> 00:28:30,250
az emetser, oder bahaltn zikh ergets, oder nemen ergets a shtikl broyt.

515
00:28:30,327 --> 00:28:32,531
oyf di felder undz getribn.

516
00:28:32,942 --> 00:28:38,926
toyznter kilometers iz men gegangen. di hitsn ⟨in⟩ zenen geven zeyer groyse;

517
00:28:39,591 --> 00:28:41,780
s'hot gebrent di erd.

518
00:28:42,055 --> 00:28:45,840
keyn trunk hot keyner nit gehat a kap vaser tsu nemen.

519
00:28:46,138 --> 00:28:48,427
di kinder, ile hobn geveynt.

520
00:28:50,340 --> 00:28:52,207
un m'hot undz getribn

521
00:28:53,125 --> 00:28:59,470
in der Ukrayne arayn. tsugetribn hot men undz biz MOGILЁV-PODOL'SK, keyn Molev.

522
00:28:58,761 --> 00:29:00,915
mir'n zikh opshteln oyf a vayle

523
00:29:00,972 --> 00:29:04,280
tsu makhn an iberrays, tsu beytn, be-

524
00:29:02,119 --> 00:29:04,200
yo. yo.

525
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:05,150
dem TAPE.

